steps.html_instructions: Head northeast on Helena Ave toward N Rodney St
Slight right onto Boulder Ave
Take the 1st right onto N Montana Ave

Turn left onto I-15BUS S/US-12 E/11th Ave (signs for I-15 E/US-287 E)
Continue to follow I-15BUS S/US-12 E
Merge onto I-15 S via the ramp to Butte
Take the exit onto I-15 S/I-90 W toward Butte
Take exit 121 for I-15 S toward Dillon/Idaho Falls

Continue onto I-15 S
Entering Idaho
Take exit 72 for I-86 W toward Twin Falls
Continue onto I-86 W
Continue onto I-84
Take exit 182 for State Route 50 toward Kimberly/Twin Falls
Turn left onto ID-50 S
Continue onto U.S. 30 W/Kimberly Rd
Turn left onto N 3000 E/Blue Lakes Blvd S
Turn right onto E 3600 N
E 3600 N turns slightly left and becomes ID-74 S

Slight left onto US-93 S
Entering Nevada
Turn right to merge onto I-80 W
Take exit 48 toward I-80BUS W/US-95 ALT/Truck Inn Way

Turn left onto I-80BUS W/US-95 ALT/Truck Inn Way (signs for Fernley/Yerington/Carson City)
Continue to follow I-80BUS W/US-95 ALT
At the traffic circle, take the 2nd exit onto Farm District Rd
Turn right onto Cottonwood Ln
Turn left onto US-50 ALT W/US-95 ALT S

Turn right onto US 30/US-50 W/California Emigrant Trail
Continue to follow US 30/US-50 W
Continue straight onto E William St
Turn left onto N Carson St
